<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12206b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12206b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12206b"> 206(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Erreur! <small>Orange</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n12206b"> <li>FW unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">(from Chapter XIII, <i>Justice et v&eacute;rit&eacute;</i>, the story <i>Comment on risque de condamner l&apos;innocent pour le coupable</i>): Ils pouss&egrave;rent plus avant et rencontr&egrave;rent un champ. Le cam&eacute;l&eacute;on dit: &ldquo;Incendions ce champ!&rdquo; Le singe dit: &ldquo;Non, je refuse.&rdquo; Le cam&eacute;l&eacute;on dit: &ldquo;<mark>Erreur!</mark> nous allons l&apos;incendier.&rdquo; <br><font color="green">[They pushed forwards and came to a field. The chameleon said: &ldquo;Let&apos;s burn the field!&rdquo; The monkey said: &ldquo;No, I refuse.&rdquo; The chameleon said: &ldquo;Mistake! We are going to burn it.&rdquo;]</font> <small> Maurice Delafosse, <a name="LNEG" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#LNEG"><cite title="source">L'&acirc;me n&egrave;gre</cite></a> (1922) 101</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
